hopobject.body: I'd like to speak to someone about a mortgage acetaminophen vs ibuprofen fever reducer Torrential storms poured four to eight inches of rain, depending on the location, on the Waynesville area.  Roubidoux Creek and Mitchell Creek raged out of their banks, flooding streets and buildings.   A boy, believed to be 4 years old, died when the car in which he was riding with his mother was washed away from a street near Mitchell Creek between the Price Cutter grocery store and Waynesville Middle School.   Searchers, including divers, were still looking for his mother on Tuesday afternoon.
